LINDA: No!

1778
01:44:01.985 --> 01:44:03.237
-(SHOUTS)
-(GRUNTS)

1779
01:44:04.404 --> 01:44:06.823
-(GASPS)
-(GRUNTS)

1780
01:44:06.865 --> 01:44:07.991
