(RATCHETS)

1786
01:44:16.333 --> 01:44:17.084
(CLICKS)

1787
01:44:19.086 --> 01:44:21.421
Ow! Fuck!

1788
01:44:21.463 --> 01:44:22.839
-(GROANS)
-(SHOUTS)

